Package: rfaScrape
Title: Scrape and export sqlite files from RFA
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Dan", "McGraw", , "daniel.e.mcgraw@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),comment = c("P.E., USACE RMC", ORCID = "0009-0006-4859-0179"))
Description: A system to scrape and export RFA project data from rfa.sqlite files
    using the `DBI` and `RSQLite` packages. Provide the path to the RFA .sqlite file
    and `rfaScrape` will read the file and export the data to organized
    directories. This package will support 'rfaR' in the future.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
